data.description: Come see your newly renovated home in the heart of Mt. Greenwood.  This 3 bed, 1.5 story brick cape cod boasts hardwood floors throughout.  Updated kitchen and bathrooms.  Partially finished basement with half bath and separate shower.  Long asphalt side drive leads to the 2 car sized concreted pad  -- ready for your garage/carport. Large fenced-in backyard with 12x12 wooded deck.  Schedule your showing today!!!
